The '''Baobab HoloNet''' was created by [[Ebenn Q3 Baobab/Legends|Ebenn Q3 Baobab]] during the times after the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]] had fallen and the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] had risen. Baobab wished to create an alternative to the [[HoloNet/Legends|HoloNet]], which was controlled by Imperial forces and only broadcast propaganda showing the Empire in a positive light. The Baobab alternative was largely abandoned and forgotten after the fall of the Empire, however, as more mainstream media outlets resumed regular broadcasting.

The recipe for [[Wookiee-ookiee]]s had leaked from [[Kashyyyk/Legends|Kashyyyk]] to the rest of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] via the Baobab HoloNet.

